==製作==
該片在2013年2月5日新聞報道指出，{{link-en|漢威電影|HanWay|}}為主要藍印影業（Blueprint Pictures）由編寫{{link-en|蘿拉·瓦德|Lauda Wade|}}著''{{link-en|上流社會的傢伙|Posh|}}''，由BFI電影基金和{{link-en|Film4 Productions|Film4 Productions|}}所提供資助予{{link-en|格雷咸姆·布德貝特|Graham Broadben|}}和Peter Czernin（彼德·克茲尼年）<ref name=Lone>{{cite news|last=Wiseman|first=Andreas|title=HanWay gets Posh for Blueprint and Lone Scherfig|url=http://www.screendaily.com/news/hanway-gets-posh-for-blueprint-and-lone-scherfig/5051427.article|accessdate=4 February 2014|newspaper=screendaily.com|date=5 February 2013|archive-date=2021-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210503125401/https://www.screendaily.com/news/hanway-gets-posh-for-blueprint-and-lone-scherfig/5051427.article|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，在2013年3月15日，該片暫時由[[羅伯·派汀森|羅伯·派汀森]]（退出）、[[麥斯·艾恩斯|麥斯·艾恩斯]]、[[山姆·克拉弗林|山姆·克拉弗林]] 和[[道格拉斯·布斯|道格拉斯·布斯]]參演<ref>{{cite news|last=Lyttelton|first=Oliver|title=Robert Pattinson, Sam Claflin, Max Irons & Douglas Booth Circling Lone Scherfig's Adaptation Of Stage Hit 'Posh'|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/robert-pattinson-sam-claflin-max-irons-douglas-booth-circling-lone-scherfigs-adaptation-of-stage-hit-posh-20130315|accessdate=4 February 2014|newspaper=indiewire.com|date=15 March 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221194955/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/robert-pattinson-sam-claflin-max-irons-douglas-booth-circling-lone-scherfigs-adaptation-of-stage-hit-posh-20130315|archive-date=2014-02-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，[[麥斯·艾恩斯|麥斯·艾恩斯]]正式參演<ref name=Max>{{cite news|last=Schillaci|first=Sophie|title='The Host's' Max Irons Headed to 'Posh'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hosts-max-irons-headed-posh-429303|accessdate=4 February 2014|newspaper=hollywoodreporter.com|date=17 March 2013|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023064500/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/hosts-max-irons-headed-posh-429303|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年5月19日，[[山姆·克拉弗林|山姆·克拉弗林]] 和[[道格拉斯·布斯|道格拉斯·布斯]]正式參演該片<ref name=Sam>{{cite news|title='Catching Fire' Star Sam Claflin Joins Lone Sherfig's 'Posh'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-catching-fire-star-sam-525226|accessdate=4 February 2014|newspaper=hollywoodreporter.com|date=19 May 2013|archive-date=2020-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200831042858/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-catching-fire-star-sam-525226|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年5月20日，[[環球影業|環球影業]]正式收購英國和愛爾蘭版權<ref>{{cite news|last=Wiseman|first=Andreas|title=Universal takes UK, Irish rights to Lone Scherfig's Posh|url=http://www.screendaily.com/festivals/cannes/upi-gets-posh-as-cast-gathers/5056447.article|accessdate=4 February 2014|newspaper=screendaily.com|date=20 May 2013|archive-date=2017-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917032735/https://www.screendaily.com/festivals/cannes/upi-gets-posh-as-cast-gathers/5056447.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年7月11日，[[納塔莉·多莫|納塔莉·多莫]] 也參演該片活動<ref name=Natalie>{{cite news|title=Natalie Dormer Cast In ‘Posh’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/carter-jenkins-melissa-benoist-natalie-dormer/|accessdate=4 February 2014|newspaper=deadline.com|date=11 July 2013|archive-date=2014-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418002004/http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/carter-jenkins-melissa-benoist-natalie-dormer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==拍攝和市場==
該片由2013年6月30日於[[英國|英國]][[牛津|牛津]]拍攝<ref>{{cite news|last=Krol|first=Charlotte|title=Max comes home to shoot new movie|url=http://www.oxfordmail.co.uk/news/10517495.Swoon_ahead__Max_comes_home_to_shoot_new_movie/|accessdate=3 February 2014|newspaper=oxfordmail.co.uk|date=1 July 2013|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401163142/https://www.oxfordmail.co.uk/news/10517495.Swoon_ahead__Max_comes_home_to_shoot_new_movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它們拍攝場景包括{{link-en|瑪格佩巷|Magpie Lane, Oxford|}}<ref name=radiotimes-shoot>{{cite news|title=Max Irons shooting new film Posh in Oxford|url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2013-07-01/max-irons-shooting-new-film-posh-in-oxford|accessdate=3 February 2014|newspaper=radiotimes.com|date=1 July 2013|archive-date=2016-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160201212059/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2013-07-01/max-irons-shooting-new-film-posh-in-oxford|dead-url=no}}</ref>、松木拍攝影基地和[[温切斯特公学|温切斯特公学]]。

而該片市場於2014年5月16日發行<ref>{{cite news|last1=KANG|first1=INKOO|title=Trailer Watch: Peek Inside the Hallowed Halls of Lone Scherfig's The Riot Club|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/womenandhollywood/trailer-watch-peek-inside-the-hallowed-halls-of-lone-scherfigs-the-riot-club-20140730|accessdate=August 1, 2014|publisher=indiewire.com|date=May 13, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140802112315/http://blogs.indiewire.com/womenandhollywood/trailer-watch-peek-inside-the-hallowed-halls-of-lone-scherfigs-the-riot-club-20140730|archive-date=2014-08-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

